Subject: Re: [T2] fuel pump/FI question of the day

That is the correct operation.  When the engine first kicks over the 
flap of the air flow sensor will move slightly to where it now contacts 
the plate and signal is sent to the double relay to power the fuel pump.
the pump should not run in acc position.
jimt
